📦 sockets 🏠

💭 Simple echo server listening on port 8888
🏁 ➡️ 🔢 🍇

	💭Starts listening on 8888
	🍺🆕🏄 8888❗️ ➡️ server
	😀🔤Started listener on 8888🔤❗

	🔁👍🍇
		💭 Opens socket with client
		🍺 🙋 server❗️ ➡️ clientSocket
		🛂🆕🧵 🍇 🎍🥡
			🔁👍🍇
				💭Read 1024 bytes
				🆗 data 👂 clientSocket 1024❗️ 🍇
					🍺 💬 clientSocket data❗️
					🔡📏data❓❗ ➡ length
					😀🔤length read: 🧲length🧲❌n❌n🔤❗
					😀 🍺 🔡 data❗️❗️
					↪❎🤜length 🙌 🔤0🔤 🤛❗🍇
						😀🔤end reached🔤❗
						↩↩
					🍉
				🍉 🙅‍♀️ error 🍇
					😀🔤Error🔤❗
				🍉
			🍉
			😀🔤Closing socket🔤❗
			🚪clientSocket❗️
		🍉❗❗
	🍉
	😀🔤End of server code❗❗❗🔤❗
	↩ 0
